      <p>Please call <a class="color-email" href="tel:+441412044041">+44 (0)141 204 4041</a>.</p>
      <p class="short-line">Strictly in&nbsp<span class="strong-text">emergencies only</span>&nbspcall David Hunter, Consul: <a class="color-email" href="tel:+447767432203">+44 (0)7767 432 203</a>.</p>
      <p>Please note that Passport renewal and visa enquiries are not treated as emergencies.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

